# Scoped ignore for the adapters-agent image build (BuildKit honors
# <Dockerfile>.dockerignore). Keep the context to source only: install deps and
# build fresh inside the image so the result is deterministic and doesn't depend
# on (or inherit corruption from) the host/CI working tree.
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/dist-lib
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.next
**/.venv
**/*.log
artifacts
**/coverage
